{"title":"backdrop-filter毛玻璃效果","slug":"backdrop-filter毛玻璃效果","date":"2020-07-15T03:26:55.000Z","updated":"2023-11-06T14:15:17.982Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/backdrop-filter毛玻璃效果.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715113252.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715111850.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715114933.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715114251.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715114632.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715115222.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715120111.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715121000.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715121540.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"backdrop-filter是什么\"><a href=\"#backdrop-filter是什么\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"backdrop-filter是什么\"></a>backdrop-filter是什么</h2><ul>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:yellow\">跟filter类似,属性设置一样,不过它适用元素背后元素</span></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715113252.png\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715111850.png\" alt=\"2\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这种效果在苹果中很常见,最早也只有在<code>safari</code>浏览器兼容<br>通过这个属性,可以很简单地创建毛玻璃效果</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>然而普通的filter一旦应用,所有元素都会受影响,比如字体也看不清</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715114933.png\" alt=\"3\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>通过backdrop-filter可以很好解决问题</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"本站应用此效果\"><a href=\"#本站应用此效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本站应用此效果\"></a>本站应用此效果</h2><ul>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715114251.png\" alt=\"4\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715114632.png\" alt=\"5\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>但是你可能看不到此效果,因为此特性兼容性不太好</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>通过查询<code>can i use</code>,可以看到基本国产浏览器都不支持,firefox也必须手动开启特性才能看到</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715115222.png\" alt=\"6\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>chrome很好的支持了,nice~</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"兼容性\"><a href=\"#兼容性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"兼容性\"></a>兼容性</h2><ul>\n<li><p>经过试验,的确firefox看不到,很影响阅读</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715120111.png\" alt=\"7\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:red\">所以不兼容的请手动点网站右下角设置开启<code>夜间模式</code>,以免影响阅读</span></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>其他手机浏览器,chrome内核的基本都支持,qq浏览器等不支持.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"毛玻璃其他解决方案\"><a href=\"#毛玻璃其他解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"毛玻璃其他解决方案\"></a>毛玻璃其他解决方案</h2><p>其他方法可能兼容性更高,就查找了几篇</p>\n<h3 id=\"纯css实现\"><a href=\"#纯css实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"纯css实现\"></a>纯css实现</h3><ul>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gentlemanhu/public-store/images/20200715121000.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>效果也是不错的,不过需要绝对布局</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://codepen.io/AmJustSam/full/ModORY/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">在线源码演示</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>根据需求可以改改</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"用js库实现\"><a href=\"#用js库实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"用js库实现\"></a>用js库实现</h3><ul>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/niklasvh/html2canvas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">html2canvas</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src= \"/img/loading.gif\" data-src=\"https: